data.description: Charming Single-Story Home with Pool in Ideal Location!  Welcome to this elegant single-story home strategically positioned between Commercial Blvd and I95 in Fort Lauderdale. The open design seamlessly connects the living room to a covered outdoor terrace and a spacious backyard with a pool. The kitchen is bright and inviting, and the three bedrooms are comfortable. The property's versatile use as a successful short-term vacation rental (Airbnb) adds value. Plus, it's conveniently close to Royal Palm Park, DRV PNK Station, Harrah's Pompano Beach casino, and more. Don't miss this unique opportunity! Contact us today for a showing!
